		<ab><lb n="1"/><w lemma="ΧΜΓ">ΧΜΓ</w> <lb n="2"/><w lemma="θεός"><persName key="God" type="divine"><expan><abbr>Θ</abbr><ex>ε</ex><abbr>ὲ</abbr></expan></persName></w> <w lemma="βοηθέω">βοήθι</w>.</ab>
      </div>
         <div>
            <p>l. 1, perhaps <foreign xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" xsl:lang="grc">
                  <persName key="Christ" type="divine" full="yes">
                     <expan>
                        <abbr>Χ</abbr>
                        <supplied reason="abbreviation">ριστὸν</supplied>
                     </expan>
                  </persName>
                  <persName key="Mary" type="divine" full="yes">
                     <expan>
                        <abbr>Μ</abbr>
                        <supplied reason="abbreviation">αρία</supplied>
                     </expan>
                  </persName>
                  <expan>
                     <abbr>Γ</abbr>
                     <supplied reason="abbreviation">εννᾷ</supplied>
                  </expan>
               </foreign>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>
               <seg cert="low">M<supplied reason="abbreviation">ary</supplied> b<supplied reason="abbreviation">ore</supplied> Ch<supplied reason="abbreviation">rist</supplied>
               </seg>. God, help.</ab>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>See discussion at <ref type="eAla-text" n="VIII.20" target=".xml"/>, and compare <ref type="inscription" n="31" target="030008.xml"/>.ii.</p>
